<h3>Q: My old thumbnails are wrong size, how do I fix it?</h3>
<p>A: You need to install the Regenerate Thumbnails plugin and run it once to create the new thumbnail sizes required for this theme.</p>
<p><strong><a class="thickbox" href="<?php echo admin_url('plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&plugin=regenerate-thumbnails&TB_iframe=true&width=640&height=320'); ?>">Install</a></strong> &middot; <a target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/regenerate-thumbnails/">Regenerate Thumbnails</a></p>

